            "text": "<$action-sendmessage $message="tm-edit-tiddler" $param=<<currentTiddler>>/>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/sq/links-context-menu/menuitems/new-window": {
            "title": "$:/plugins/sq/links-context-menu/menuitems/new-window",
            "sq-contextmenu-name": "Open in new window",
            "tags": "$:/tags/links-context-menu/menuitems",
            "text": "<$action-sendmessage $message="tm-open-window" $param=<<currentTiddler>>/>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/sq/links-context-menu/readme": {
            "title": "$:/plugins/sq/links-context-menu/readme",
            "text": "@@color:red;''Highly experimental - no support available. Use at your own risk.''@@

* Adds an extensible and customisable context menu for links to tiddlers.
* Display the browser default contextmenu by using the <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> key.
* Add entries to the menu by adding tiddlers with the tag <<tag $:/tags/links-context-menu/menuitems>>
** For an example see [[$:/plugins/sq/links-context-menu/menuitems/new-window]]

//Screenshot://

